Description: Prepare for GCC 15 defaults (C23) and fix security issues
 Replace multi-character character constants ('TBL1', 'TBL3') with explicit
 hexadecimal values to avoid implementation-defined behaviour warned about
 under C23.
 Replace deprecated tempnam() with mkstemp()+fdopen() to avoid the
 dangerous temp-file race condition (CWE-377).
 Fix int<->pointer casts in PushExe/PopExe to use uintptr_t.
 Make swindow[] static in lzss.c to avoid polluting the global namespace.
 Add missing #include <unistd.h> and <stdint.h>.
Generated-by: Claude Sonnet 4.6
Reviewed-by: Nicolas HOUDELOT <nicolas@demosdebs.org>
Applied-Upstream: no
Last-Update: 2026-05-03
